Author: K0B3ryant
Text: I’m so vain it’s truly shameful so the mirrors are what I obsess over.   But let a skinner chick (not hard to be) walk in and I hate myself immediately lol

Author: AfterSense
Text: if i'm in the wrong head space i cry after the gym too. it's all those mirrors. all the equipment at my gym faces the same wall, which is just one giant mirror. there are a few treadmills that have equipment in front of them so you can't see yourself in the mirror and if i don't get to use one of those i have an anxiety attack in the locker room from staring at myself running for 40 minutes.
